Class Source.SourceBuilder<Builder,​Src extends Source>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.millicast.Source.SourceBuilder<Builder,​Src>
  • Type Parameters:
    Builder - The source type builder used to build a source object derived from the Source class
    Src - The actual source type (VideoSource, AudioSource, AudioPlayback)
    Direct Known Subclasses:

    Source
    public static class Source.SourceBuilder<Builder,​Src extends Source>
extends java.lang.Object
    The source builder is used to build a source object. It uses a CRTP design to build sources according to their real type (derived from Source)
